	<tr>
	
		<td class="msg_user_cell" width="150" valign=top>
		
			 









<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=44655'  class="auth_text"  style="font-weight:bold;" >	
<span style='color:#9933FF;font-weight:bold; '>Tastian</span></a>
			<br>
			
			<span style="font-size: 8pt;">
			Community Correspondent<br>
			
				Posts: 1066<br>
				
				Registered: 06-19-2004
				
			</span>
			


			
			<br>
			
				<img src="/i/p.gif" height=8 width=150 border=0 alt=""><br>
				
			<a href='/eq/view_profile?user.id=44655'>







</a><br>
			


			
			<p>
			






<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
Reply <a href="/eq/board/message?board.id=beastlordbalance&message.id=3283#M3283">1</a> of 25
</span>

			<br><img src="/i/p.gif" width=1 height=6><br>
			<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
			
					Viewed 725 times<br>
					
			</span>
			
		</td>
		
		<td rowspan=2 bgcolor="#050A0E" width=1><img src="/i/p.gif" height=1 width=1 border=0 alt=""><br></td>
	
		<td colspan=2 class="msg_text_cell" width="100%" valign=top style="text-align: justify; 
		
				background-color: #050A0E; 
				
				 background-image: none;
				 
				background-repeat: repeat-x;
				" 
			>
			The issue of haste duration, haste potions, etc has come up for awhile among beastlords.  It has even been mentioned on the top 10 a few times as I recall.  Some want a group version, some are ok with the thought of longer duration, but there is another issue that I think we need to go over first.  <br><br>Are you willing to see an increase in the mana cost of haste if it receives some upgrade(s)?<br><br>The change might not be % for % even, or it might be, or it might not even happen.  I just need to be sure that most beastlords understand that the mana cost likely would increase (especially if this goes to group) and that they still want such a change before I go further with this issue.	
		</td></tr>
		<tr>
		
		<td class="msg_date_cell" valign=bottom nowrap>
		<span style="font-size: 8pt; font-weight: normal;">
		 <span class=date_text>11-04-2005</span> <span class=time_text>09:12 AM</span>
		</span>
		</td>

		
			<td colspan=2 class="msg_rating_cell" valign=bottom nowrap 
			
				style="background-color: #050A0E;"
				
			>
			
				&nbsp;
				
				<br><br><a href="javascript:lipopup('/eq/notification?board.id=beastlordbalance&message.id=3283&notification.type=1', 'notification', 600, 460, 'yes', 'yes')" class=text_smallest><u>Report Abuse to a Moderator</u></a>
				
		</td>
			
		</tr>
